<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{title}}</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Russo+One&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: beige;
            font-family: 'Russo One', sans-serif;
        }

        body::after {
            content: "";
            background-color: pink;
            background-size: cover;
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 40px;
            z-index: -1;
        }

        .container {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        #imagem-radio {
            position: absolute;
            border: 5px;
            border-radius: 1000px;
            top: 20px;
            left: 20px;
            width: 150px;
        }

        .link-titulo {
            color: inherit;
            transition: color 0.3s ease, font-size 0.3s ease;
        }

        .link-titulo:hover {
            color: #ff0000;
            font-size: larger;
        }

        .botoes {
            background-color: pink;
        }

        .botoes a:hover {
            color: black;
            font-size: larger;
        }
    </style>

</head>

<body>
    <img id="imagem-radio" src="/img/radio.png" alt="imagem radio">

    <div class="container my-2">

        <div class="row text-center my-3">
            <div class="col-md-2 d-none d-md-block">
                <img src="/img/album2.jpg" alt="album2.jpg" class="img-fluid w-55">
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-8 my-auto">
                <h1>
                    <a href="/" style="text-decoration: none;" class="link-titulo">Melodia Analisada</a>
                </h1>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-2 d-none d-md-block">
                <img src="/img/album.jpg" alt="album.jpg" class="img-fluid w-55 ">
            </div>

            <div>
                <h2>
                    No nosso blog Melodia Analisada você e outros usuários podem compartilhar as suas notas de
                    álbuns especificos, dando suas opiniões, dizendo quais são suas faixas mais e menos curtidas e
                    mais o que você desejar!
                </h2>
            </div>

        </div>
        <div class="botoes">
            <ul class="nav nav-tabs">
                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/">Início</a>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/Sobre">Sobre o Blog</a>
                </li>
                <nav>
                    <ul>
                        {{#if usuarioId}}
                        <li>Bem-vindo, {{usuarioNome}} (ID: {{usuarioId}})!</li>
                        <li><a class="nav-link" href="/usuario/logout" onclick="return confirmDelete()">Logout</a></li>
                        <script>
                            function confirmDelete() {
                                return confirm("Você tem certeza que deseja fazer o logout?");
                            }
                        </script>
                        {{else}}
                        <li><a class="nav-link" href="/usuario/login">Login</a></li>
                        <li><a class="nav-link" href="/usuario/register">Criar Conta</a></li>
                        {{/if}}
                    </ul>
                </nav>


            </ul>
        </div>

        {{#if message}}
        <div class="alert alert-{{message.[0]}} alert-dismissible fade show my-3" role="alert">
            <strong>{{message.[1]}}</strong>
            <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="alert" aria-label="Close"></button>
        </div>
        {{/if}}
    </div>
    {{{body}}}
</body>

</html>